translated: Johansson, Ernst Wilhelm, wholesaler, Kalmar, born 4/7/86 in Karlshamn to Johan Jönsson and Carolina Åkesson. Married to Linnéa Alm in 19xx, with one child: Kerstin, born in 1926. Managing director of A-B Ev^ika, Ludvigs A-B, and Fastigh. A-B Eo’s. Vice-chairman of the board of Riksbank’s division office in Kalmar since 1939, chairman of the Kalmar merchants' association, treasurer of the Kalmar industry and commerce association, member of the Smål. and Blek. commerce committee. Vice-chairman of Dahmska Foundation, member of the board of Kalmar Art Association and Kalmar district tourist association. Awarded with the Sweden's Trade Federation's gold medal.
